NIKES BUSINESS PLANS, OBJECTIVES AND EXPECTED OPERATING RESULTS, AND THE ASSUMPTIONS UPON WHICH THOSE STATEMENTS ARE BASED, MADE OR INCORPORATED BY REFERENCE FROM TIME TO TIME BY

