MANAGEMENT PROGRAM, AND FOREIGN CURRENCY GAINS AND LOSSES RESULTING FROM THE DIFFERENCE BETWEEN ACTUAL FOREIGN CURRENCY RATES AND STANDARD RATES ASSIGNED TO THESE ENTITIES, WHICH ARE USED TO

