OUR OTHER BUSINESSES ARE COMPRISED OF OUR AFFILIATE BRANDS; COLE HAAN, CONVERSE, HURLEY AND UMBRO; AND NIKE GOLF. THE REVENUE GROWTH AT

CONVERSE WAS PRIMARILY DRIVEN BY INCREASED LICENSING REVENUE IN CHINA, AS

