TABLE OF CONTENTS

WELL AS INCREASED SALES IN THE U.K. AS WE TRANSITIONED THAT MARKET TO A CONVERSE OWNED DISTRIBUTION MODEL. REVENUES FOR COLE HAAN INCREASED 12%, DRIVEN BY DOUBLE-DIGIT PERCENTAGE GROWTH IN OUR

