PLANS AVAILABLE TO U.S.-BASED EMPLOYEES. THE COMPANY MATCHES A PORTION OF EMPLOYEE CONTRIBUTIONS. COMPANY CONTRIBUTIONS TO THE SAVINGS PLANS WERE $39 MILLION, $34 MILLION, AND $38 MILLION FOR THE

YEARS ENDED MAY 31, 2011, 2010, AND 2009, RESPECTIVELY, AND ARE INCLUDED IN SELLING AND ADMINISTRATIVE EXPENSE.

